Package: DetLifeInsurance
Type: Package
Title: Life Insurance Premium and Reserves Valuation
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joaquin", "Auza", email = "auzajoaquin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Maria Sol", "Alvarez", email = "alvarezmmsol@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Joaquin Auza <auzajoaquin@gmail.com>
Description: Methods for valuation of life insurance premiums and reserves (including variable-benefit and fractional coverage). It also contains functions for 
    equivalent interest/discount rate calculation, present and future values of annuities, and loan amortization schedule.
